data.description: UPDATED 4 Bedroom 3 Full Bathroom home located in the BEAUTIFUL Deerfield Subdivision!! SOARING ceilings, open floor plan, gas fireplace, & formal dining room! BRAND NEW carpet & luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout main floor & bedrooms. The kitchen includes granite counter tops, large pantry, Stainless steel appliances & real hardwood floors. The master suite offers tray ceilings, large walk-in closet, double vanity, separate shower & jetted tub. Entertaining in mind with the large fenced backyard. Walkout basement with family room(wired for theater), wet bar, and 4th bedroom & 3rd full bathroom. Located near golf course & sports complex. This well kept home provides easy access to downtown and Whiteman AFB. Call today to schedule a showing.
